text: Nancy Faeser (born 13 July 1970) is a German lawyer and politician of the Social Democratic Party (SPD). She was the Federal Minister of the Interior and Community in Chancellor Olaf Scholz's cabinet from 2021 to 2025. She was a member of the State Parliament of Hesse from 2003 until 2021. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Hesse Category:Interior ministers of Germany
